# Lab 01 — Resource Groups, Tags & Budget Alert

## What I Did
- Created Resource Groups via Portal and CLI
- Applied tags (Environment, Owner, CostCenter)
- Created Budget Alert at $10 threshold

## CLI Commands Used
az group create --name myRG --location eastus

az tag create --resource-id <resource-id> \
  --tags Environment=Dev Owner=Sahana

## What I Learned
- Tags help organize and track costs
- Budget alerts notify before overspending
- Resource Groups are containers for resources

## AZ-104 Exam Topic
- Manage Azure identities and governance
